  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/d4e70cd73a7d2263293742833466c20c.avif?t=1768885695\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ BREW UP SOME ACTION ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brew up some action in this coffee-powered sequel to the hit musical shooter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PopSlinger Vol. 2 – Loveless</strong> is a <i>narrative-focused, musical shooter</i> inspired by the bold spirit of ‘80s and ‘90s New Retro culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ A NEW MISSION BEGINS ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Agent <strong>Cooper McLaren</strong> of the <i>Juncture Against Various Anomalies (JAVA)</i> teams up with <strong>Akane 2.0</strong>, a reformed digital idol, on a daring rescue: find <strong>Ria</strong>, the heroine of the first game, who has mysteriously vanished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/8561ccdf845d45327339516dd392068f.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/8561ccdf845d45327339516dd392068f.webm?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/489ba83d12da19d58c6043beed5edd18.webp?t=1768885695\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/489ba83d12da19d58c6043beed5edd18.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=250 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As they descend into the surreal <strong>Purple District</strong>, Cooper’s coffee-fueled firepower and Akane’s data-driven abilities will be tested against the enigmatic <strong>Loveless Sisters</strong>—and a host of strange new enemies that pulse to the rhythm of chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/e89241084f85f9ec73a08f373d3666ef.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/e89241084f85f9ec73a08f373d3666ef.webm?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/c99b0dbc2fa4434465745460b40b7926.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/c99b0dbc2fa4434465745460b40b7926.webm?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/068dd7489cf7723e1bcab6713e0b503f.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/068dd7489cf7723e1bcab6713e0b503f.webm?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ STYLE AND STORY COLLIDE ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☕ <strong>Upgraded Visuals:</strong> Dive into a vibrant world of New Retro animation inspired by classic ‘90s cartoons and anime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎙️ <strong>Fully Voiced Drama:</strong> Every scene comes alive with expressive voice acting and dynamic cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌀 <strong>Expanded Narrative:</strong> Explore a deeper, more emotional story exploring connection, identity, and family amid the neon storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ COFFEE-FUELED COMBAT ▼</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summon & Stun:</strong> Unleash new enemy-stunning summons for crowd-control flair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dream Time 2.0:</strong> An upgraded action bar integrates your Dream Time system for seamless rhythm-combat flow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Color-Switching Foes:</strong> Adapt fast to enemies that shift hues—and strategies—on the fly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black & White Variants:</strong> New enemies that force precise timing and tactical balance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/c48fe3bb1ac72982621859683c109923.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/c48fe3bb1ac72982621859683c109923.webm?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/c48fe3bb1ac72982621859683c109923.mp4?t=1768885695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▼ GROOVE THROUGH THE CHAOS ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶Every encounter in <i>PopSlinger Vol. 2 – Loveless</i> moves to the beat.🎶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An <strong>expanded, reactive soundtrack</strong> fuses <i>Future Funk, French House, Rave,</i> and <i>Pop Punk</i>, dynamically syncing to your performance—every blast, dodge, and summon turns combat into a living remix.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From <strong>shrine-like baseball stadiums</strong> to <strong>Thunderdome-esque kingdoms</strong>, each stage bursts with color, challenge, and New Retro attitude—wilder, louder, and flashier than ever. 💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/a81607eba945528dac6daaff657f410c.avif?t=1768885695\" width=1138 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In <i>PopSlinger Vol. 2 – Loveless</i>, enemies don’t just fall — they <i>pop</i> to the beat!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your coffee blaster to hit enemies with the <strong>matching color</strong> to keep the rhythm alive.<br>🎯 <strong>Land 4 shots of the same color</strong> to trigger <strong>Akane Access!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/d50b000a2870987e3a5500e6db4b1703.webp?t=1768885695\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/d50b000a2870987e3a5500e6db4b1703.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=194 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Pop 8 enemies in two matching sets</strong> to create a <strong>Color Combo!</strong> — this makes the <i>music change</i> and the world around you pulse in sync.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/bc622e17a333de2a7bd5de29a8ee1180.webp?t=1768885695\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/bc622e17a333de2a7bd5de29a8ee1180.poster.avif?t=1768885695\" class=\"bb_img\" width=425 height=257 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the chain going!<br>☕ <strong>8 of the same color = Double Combo!</strong><br>🌈 <strong>Stack combos</strong> to charge your <strong>Special Bar</strong>, light it up, and unleash <strong>Dream Time!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more combos you pull off, the better the <strong>grooves</strong> — and your <strong>Rankman Level</strong> — will climb.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195370/extras/24f4c690dfe6ef021954f851c4c9eed4.avif?t=1768885695\" width=425 height=257 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 <i>Your flow determines the ending… and the ultimate remix of your destiny.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PopSlinger Vol. 2 – Loveless</strong> is your ticket to a <strong>funky, coffee-powered adventure like no other!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☕ <strong>Developed by Funky Can Creative — Creators of PopSlinger (2022)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
